Description:
    This generator is used to help automate some of the
    wiring needed to create a new language version of
    "To Change Everything".

Example 1:
    rails generate to_change_everything es espanol

    This will create:
      insert  app/controllers/to_change_everything_controller.rb
      create  app/assets/stylesheets/to_change_everything/_espanol.scss
      append  app/assets/stylesheets/to_change_everything.scss
      create  config/locales/to_change_everything/es.yml

Example 2:
    rails generate to_change_everything fa فارسی rtl

    This will create:
      insert  app/controllers/to_change_everything_controller.rb
      create  app/assets/stylesheets/to_change_everything/_فارسی.scss
      append  app/assets/stylesheets/to_change_everything.scss
      create  config/locales/to_change_everything/fa.yml
